room_title: Escape room "Locked In Time" by MindGames of Mebane in Mebane
room_description:
Scientists at the University of Mebane have finally accomplished the impossible. They have build a machine that will travel through time. Intern Zev was sent back to 1976. No one has seen or heard from him since.
The scientists are very concerned that there has been contamination of the timeline. You, the new interns, have reluctantly volunteered to be sent back and find Zev and the contamination. Now the machine only has enough juice for one hour. can you make it back in time?
